{"title": "Negou a pris\u00e3o da casa de Ilaria Salis, ainda nas correntes \"tratadas como um cachorro!\" Ele denuncia o pai, enquanto o tribunal \u00e9 uma faccia nazista do lado de fora dos advogados e solidariedade", "published time": "2024-03-28T21:09:00+08:00", "images": ["https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqXbDurj_5R3Xu2R5nooUveiam-tLolDZtSyFHp2K0BIbAzaWLl5N2S8BebfseY03WSrSSaO0wp9kDjNQVJ07I7f8OyTNhKyl1xYsWpiciBEljAXjbmj4CNjsylVLGLs8q4mLZbZojrO-fp10vdh2TknhpgJmWRdrD_inxnLfsVlGw-cxJs2gloP011sWy/s700/40939cf811c4df8070257be4a0d7823c.jpeg"], "content": "<div class=\"post-body entry-content\" id=\"post-body-2473584618480106179\" itemprop=\"description articleBody\">\n <div style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: #080808; font-family: Verdana; padding: 3px 6px;\">\n  <h1 class=\"post-single-title\" style='-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; color: var(--ink); font-family: \"Suisse Intl Web\", \"Suisse Intl Web Fallback\", Arial, sans-serif; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0px 0px 0px -0.05em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: balance;'>\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.02em; white-space-collapse: initial;\">\n    A pris\u00e3o da casa negada, Ilaria Salis permanece na c\u00e9lula. Na sala de aula ainda com algemas e correntes\n   </span>\n  </h1>\n  <div style=\"\">\n   <span face='\"Suisse Intl Web\", \"Suisse Intl Web Fallback\", Arial, sans-serif' style=\"color: #393745;  letter-spacing: -0.38px;\">\n    A pr\u00f3xima audi\u00eancia foi marcada em 24 de maio.\n   </span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both;  text-align: center;\">\n   <img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"467\" data-original-width=\"700\" height=\"426\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqXbDurj_5R3Xu2R5nooUveiam-tLolDZtSyFHp2K0BIbAzaWLl5N2S8BebfseY03WSrSSaO0wp9kDjNQVJ07I7f8OyTNhKyl1xYsWpiciBEljAXjbmj4CNjsylVLGLs8q4mLZbZojrO-fp10vdh2TknhpgJmWRdrD_inxnLfsVlGw-cxJs2gloP011sWy/s700/40939cf811c4df8070257be4a0d7823c.jpeg\" srcset=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiqXbDurj_5R3Xu2R5nooUveiam-tLolDZtSyFHp2K0BIbAzaWLl5N2S8BebfseY03WSrSSaO0wp9kDjNQVJ07I7f8OyTNhKyl1xYsWpiciBEljAXjbmj4CNjsylVLGLs8q4mLZbZojrO-fp10vdh2TknhpgJmWRdrD_inxnLfsVlGw-cxJs2gloP011sWy/s700/40939cf811c4df8070257be4a0d7823c.jpeg\" width=\"640\"/>\n  </div>\n  <span face='\"Suisse Intl Web\", \"Suisse Intl Web Fallback\", Arial, sans-serif' style=\"color: #393745;  letter-spacing: -0.38px;\">\n   \"A en\u00e9sima prova de for\u00e7a do governo orbano\", comentou ele\n  </span>\n  <span face='\"Suisse Intl Web\", \"Suisse Intl Web Fallback\", Arial, sans-serif' style=\"color: #393745;  font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.38px;\">\n   Roberto Salis\n  </span>\n  <span face='\"Suisse Intl Web\", \"Suisse Intl Web Fallback\", Arial, sans-serif' style=\"color: #393745;  letter-spacing: -0.38px;\">\n   , o pai da mulher. \"Eu esperava um pouco - ele acrescentou - Ilaria aqui \u00e9 considerado um grande perigo\". \"Nossos ministros n\u00e3o causaram uma boa impress\u00e3o e o governo italiano deve fazer um exame da consci\u00eancia\", acrescentou o pai de Ilaria. \"As correntes n\u00e3o dependem do juiz, mas do sistema penitenci\u00e1rio e, portanto, executivo e do governo italiano podem e devem fazer algo porque minha filha n\u00e3o \u00e9 tratada como um cachorro\", acrescentou.\n  </span>\n </div>\n <div style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 3px 6px;\">\n  <p style='-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; color: #393745; font-family: \"Suisse Intl Web\", \"Suisse Intl Web Fallback\", Arial, sans-serif; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit;  font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; letter-spacing: -0.38px; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0.4em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>\n   \"Cale a boca ou divida sua cabe\u00e7a\": \u00e9 o quanto um grupo de alguns extremistas de direita disse ao grupo composto pelos advogados e amigos de Ilaria Salis ap\u00f3s a chegada deles \u00e0 quadra. \"Eles nos aguardaram e nos insultaram e amea\u00e7aram para h\u00fangaro\", disse o advogado Eugenio Losco.\n  </p>\n  <p style='-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; border: 0px; color: #393745; font-family: \"Suisse Intl Web\", \"Suisse Intl Web Fallback\", Arial, sans-serif; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit;  font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; letter-spacing: -0.38px; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0.4em; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>\n   \"Eles adotaram os telefones celulares, retomaram e nosso tradutor nos disse que estava nos amea\u00e7ando\", continuou a Losco.\n  </p>\n </div>\n <div style=\"clear: both;\">\n </div>\n</div>", "pdf_content": null, "pdf_links": [], "description": "A pris\u00e3o da casa negada, Ilaria Salis permanece na c\u00e9lula. A pr\u00f3xima audi\u00eancia foi posta no tribunal com algemas e correntes. \"EU'...", "author": [], "source": "https://femminismorivoluzionario.blogspot.com/2024/03/negati-ad-ilaria-salis-gli-arresti.html", "source_name": "femminismo proletario rivoluzionario"}